  "2382380": {
    "name": "某魔法师的养猫日记",
    "steam_appid": 2382380,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法介绍</h2><br>游戏中包含了四种小游戏，分别为跑酷，睡觉，抓鱼，抓老鼠，同时也对应四种比赛。<br><br>消耗掉猫咪一些体力来玩小游戏就可以锻炼猫咪，随着猫咪能力增加游戏会变的越来越难，当猫咪能力达到一定的值就可以让猫咪参加比赛赢得奖励。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >花店经营</h2><br>开始后玩家将进入花店，花店有四个房间。大厅、卧室、猫房、花房。<br><br>花店经营时有时间的概念，将分为早上和晚上，合起来即为度过一天。通过点击界面正中间顶部的按钮可切换清晨和黄昏。<br><br>购买种子种花，每天浇水，等花卉开花后即可通过卖花赚钱。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382380/extras/5df1109cd9f82df1ee442bf27984fc16.poster.avif?t=1696332446\" width=302 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382380/extras/5df1109cd9f82df1ee442bf27984fc16.webm?t=1696332446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382380/extras/5df1109cd9f82df1ee442bf27984fc16.mp4?t=1696332446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >训练猫咪</h2><br>早上，如果猫咪体力充沛，这时候使用猫房中的“魔镜”，就可以训练猫咪。<br><br>每个小游戏都有通关条件，如果没有达到通关条件，猫咪的能力提升在结算时会减半。<br><br>如果，所有猫咪都消耗完了体力则应该喂食猫咪，可购买食物投喂猫咪。点击屏幕中间的太阳按钮进入下一天猫咪就能恢复体力。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >跑酷小游戏</h2><br>移动鼠标控制法杖去点击猫咪，用法杖放出的风之魔法接住从楼顶上掉下的猫咪。<br><br>魔法的释放有次数限制，要注意时机和节奏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382380/extras/305d3c72555a72a445ae29cd4006b516.poster.avif?t=1696332446\" width=320 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382380/extras/305d3c72555a72a445ae29cd4006b516.webm?t=1696332446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382380/extras/305d3c72555a72a445ae29cd4006b516.mp4?t=1696332446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >睡觉小游戏</h2><br>移动鼠标控制法杖去点击蚊子，消灭蚊子让猫咪睡尽可能多的时间。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >抓鱼小游戏</h2><br>移动鼠标控制法杖去吹风游过来的鱼，让猫咪接住鱼就能增加猫咪的能力。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >捕鼠小游戏</h2><br>移动鼠标控制法杖去点击隐藏在黑暗中的老师，让猫咪抓到尽可能多的老师。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >音控跑酷</h2><br>游戏中可以得到一只小奶猫，小奶猫不能进行比赛，且当其进行跑酷时，可通过<strong><u>音频输入</u></strong>来代替鼠标来控制猫咪跳跃。<br><br>此时要注意保持室内相对安静，无额外声源影响。<br><br><i>windows 10以上用户在使用音频输入前请确保在操作系统的隐私设置中允许游戏对麦克风的访问。</i><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382380/extras/86b09d034252faba1388e597c7113a55.poster.avif?t=1696332446\" width=164 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382380/extras/86b09d034252faba1388e597c7113a55.webm?t=1696332446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382380/extras/86b09d034252faba1388e597c7113a55.mp4?t=1696332446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >提供了多种与猫咪的互动</h2><br>1．找猫咪：简单的躲猫猫游戏。每天早上醒来猫咪会分散在各个屋子里，点击猫咪后猫咪会回到猫屋，方便查看哪只猫咪没在家。<br><br>2．摸猫咪：比如给猫咪喂食、猫咪做噩梦可以叫醒猫咪。<br><br>3．得到新猫咪：达到触发条件后会发生特殊事件，大厅的电脑中会拍摄到猫咪，若拍到猫咪正脸则可直接用魔法将这个猫咪召唤过来。<br><br>4．猫咪心情不好会打碎东西：打碎东西会减少猫咪血量。点击破碎物品可复原物品。易碎品的恢复需要花费金币。<br><br>5．切换房间时有概率遇到老鼠：老鼠会打破东西或者偷取食物或种子而造成破坏，老鼠遇到概率随着猫咪总量增加而减少，若当前房间正好有猫咪在则一定不会遇到老鼠。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382380/extras/12a2b93fe57a4ad60f73877dbd32ba64.poster.avif?t=1696332446\" width=320 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382380/extras/12a2b93fe57a4ad60f73877dbd32ba64.webm?t=1696332446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382380/extras/12a2b93fe57a4ad60f73877dbd32ba64.mp4?t=1696332446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你可以收集</h2><br>1．最多5只不同的猫咪！包含一只特殊的小奶猫。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382380/extras/765b913aa79b40b2878b333214fbcd37.poster.avif?t=1696332446\" width=252 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382380/extras/765b913aa79b40b2878b333214fbcd37.webm?t=1696332446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382380/extras/765b913aa79b40b2878b333214fbcd37.mp4?t=1696332446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>2．一些彩蛋，比如达到一些条件就会引来新的猫咪或者从礼物中抽取招财猫。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382380/extras/676bc72763080985b0e6e58564a0762a.poster.avif?t=1696332446\" width=480 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382380/extras/676bc72763080985b0e6e58564a0762a.webm?t=1696332446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382380/extras/676bc72763080985b0e6e58564a0762a.mp4?t=1696332446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
